ets/MiSide.jpg'), \r\n          originalPrice: 52, \r\n          discountPrice: 52, \r\n          discount: 0,\r\n          description: '你一定在各种游戏里有喜欢的女孩，如果你真的和她在一起了呢？'\r\n        },\r\n        { \r\n          title: '游戏3', \r\n          type: '射击', \r\n          image: 'path/to/game3-image.jpg', \r\n          originalPrice: 75, \r\n          discountPrice: 60, \r\n          discount: 20,\r\n          description: '这是一款紧张刺激的射击游戏，玩家需要精准射击击败敌人。'\r\n        },\r\n        { \r\n          title: '游戏3', \r\n          type: '射击', \r\n          image: 'path/to/game3-image.jpg', \r\n          originalPrice: 75, \r\n          discountPrice: 60, \r\n          discount: 20,\r\n          description: '这是一款紧张刺激的射击游戏，玩家需要精准射击击败敌人。'\r\n        },\r\n        { \r\n          title: '游戏3', \r\n          type: '射击', \r\n          image: 'path/to/game3-image.jpg', \r\n          originalPrice: 75, \r\n          discountPrice: 60, \r\n          discount: 20,\r\n          description: '这是一款紧张刺激的射击游戏，玩家需要精准射击击败敌人。'\r\n        },\r\n        { \r\n          title: '游戏3', \r\n          type: '射击', \r\n          image: 'path/to/game3-image.jpg', \r\n          originalPrice: 75, \r\n          discountPrice: 60, \r\n          discount: 20,\r\n          description: '这是一款紧张刺激的射击游戏，玩家需要精准射击击败敌人。'\r\n        },\r\n        // 添加更多游戏...\r\n      ],\r\n      currentGame: null,\r\n      descriptionTop: 0  // 新增属性\r\n    };\r\n  },\r\n  methods: {\r\n    showDescription(game, event) {\r\n      this.currentGame = game;\r\n      const gameItem = event.currentTarget;\r\n      if (gameItem) {\r\n        this.descriptionTop = gameItem.offsetTop;\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    hideDescription() {\r\n      this.currentGame = null;\r\n    },\r\n    addToCart(game) {\r\n      console.log(`将 ${game.title} 加入购物车`);\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style scoped>\r\n.home-page {\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  min-height: 100vh;\r\n  display: flex;\r\n  flex-direction: column;\r\n  align-items: center;\r\n}\r\n\